Define these shorthands:
\begin{align*}
f     & = \mean[\Gr]{\Lam{x} s} \\
\D f  & = \mean[\Gr]{\Lam{x}{\Lam{\D x}{\Derive s}}} \\
v'    & = \Apply{\D v}v,\\
\Gr_1 & = \Gr[x\mapsto v,\D x\mapsto\D v]
