\Gr_2  & = \Gr[x\mapsto v,\D x\mapsto \Diff vv],\\
\Gr_2' & = \Gr'[x\mapsto v',\D x\mapsto \Diff{v'}{v'}].
\end{align*}
It is clear that $\Gr_2'$ is the updated version of $\Gr_2$. By
